{"tid":1059104,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]00後同01記者都入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-03-13T02:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T21:58:01.000Z","uid":241832,"like":93,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fadb8f13a5280de00591df72c6c37963ff869fcb","tid":1059104,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"冇人話我啱哂 <br />\n不過呢個係我做cd rom咁耐觀察番嚟<br />\n連登仔口口聲聲話出面啲人洗腦<br />\n媒體染紅 呢個奶共<br />\n有冇諗過其實你地(我地)都做緊類似嘅野<br />\n洗緊啲00後腦<br />\n佢地心智未成熟架<br />\n真係會信哂<br />\n個個女人都係雞<br />\n個個警察係黑警<br />\n去大陸做show就係奶共<br />\n個個為咗喺呢個咁正義咁本土嘅論壇生存<br />\n走去留埋哂啲虛偽嘅言<br />\n呢啲錯誤嘅價值觀<br />\n不過可能你覺得係啱嘅<br />\n之後又放句上連登勿認真出嚟擋<br />\n大撚哂咩 個腦有冇得移除回帶先<br />\n各位比人話過係五毛嘅唔好當咗自己真係五毛<br />\n你只係同話你係五毛條友唔同意見<br />\n唔係鼓催五毛<br />\n不過班盲反真係好肉酸<br />\n<br />\n上個連登多真係壞腦"},{"pid":"20cf0a00ddb398a125b04535d13dd1d0c356f407","tid":1059104,"uid":142313,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"已經見過有人信撚哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b303bfea1d7b92033b5468f884c059b2f279b34c","tid":1059104,"uid":241832,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"20cf0a00ddb398a125b04535d13dd1d0c356f407","tid":1059104,"uid":142313,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"已經見過有人信撚哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:44:11.000Z","msg":"我都見唔少 一班人食飯傾偈竟然攞啲連登價值觀出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7456f001bdf74ffb70bed6a0572aefd093a2964f","tid":1059104,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20dea2c596b3a0e6c65f5755204018cf068b7e9c","tid":1059104,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-